---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Far Fox" description="Far Fox privacy policy. Learn how we protect your data and respect your privacy.">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 backdrop-blur-md bg-fox-bg/80 border-b border-fox-pink/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="/fox-logo.png" alt="Far Fox" class="w-8 h-8" />
        <span class="text-xl font-900 tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Far Fox
        </span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://app.lovefarfox.com"
        class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple text-white font-700 text-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-fox-pink/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Open App
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-28 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-900 tracking-tight mb-8">
        Privacy <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-fox-text-light text-sm mb-8">Last updated: March 30, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-fox-text-light leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you use Far Fox, we collect the following information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Email address and display name when you sign up.</li>
            <li><strong>Content you create:</strong> Photos, letters, question answers, mood entries, and other content you share with your partner.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> How you interact with the app, including features used, streaks, and challenge completions.</li>
            <li><strong>Device information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and timezone for delivering a personalized experience.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Provide and maintain the Far Fox app and its features.</li>
            <li>Share your content with your connected partner (and only your partner).</li>
            <li>Track streaks, XP, and fox companion progression.</li>
            <li>Send notifications about partner activity and daily prompts.</li>
            <li>Improve the app based on aggregated, anonymized usage patterns.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            Your content is shared only with your connected partner. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes. We may share data with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Our backend infrastructure provider, which hosts your data securely.</li>
            <li><strong>Vercel:</strong> Our web hosting provider for the landing page and web app.</li>
            <li><strong>Law enforcement:</strong> Only when required by law or to protect the safety of our users.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
          <p>
            Your data is stored securely using Supabase with row-level security policies. Photos and media are stored in encrypted cloud storage. We use HTTPS for all data transmission and require authentication for all API access.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Access and download your personal data.</li>
            <li>Delete your account and all associated data.</li>
            <li>Opt out of non-essential notifications.</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">6. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            The Far Fox landing page uses Vercel Web Analytics and Umami Cloud, both of which collect anonymized page view and referrer data without cookies or personal identifiers. The app itself does not use cookies or third-party tracking.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of significant changes through the app or via email.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">9. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or your data, reach out to us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@lovefarfox.com" class="text-fox-pink hover:underline">hello@lovefarfox.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-fox-pink/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <span class="font-800 text-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">Far Fox</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-fox-text-light/50">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-fox-pink transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-fox-pink transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <span>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Far Fox</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
